beer.beer_description:
Hey there, beer drinker. You know what you're looking for: a beer that's got the depth and complexity of a wine, but with the smoothness and drinkability of a lager.
You've come to the right place. We've got what you want—and more! Our Belgian Dubbel is a smokey oaked beer with aromas of spice, dark fruits and vanilla. It gives a finish of plum and toffee molasses that will leave you begging for more (even if you're not usually one for beer).

items.badge_name: Dubbel, Tripel and Quad Oh My! (Level 5)
items.badge_description: Dubbel, Tripel, or Quad, you can’t go wrong with these amazing feats of Belgian style brewing. Whether you’re looking for something light and golden or dark and boozy, one of these will do the trick! That's 25 different beers with the style of Dubbel, Tripel or Quad! Try 5 more for Level 6!

items.badge_description: Either you must be sampling or really like beer! That's 12 beers in 1 day.

At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 10 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 3! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

Round and round the wheel goes! Which style you’ll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 10 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 3!
